121
00:14:09,899 --> 00:14:13,139
[SPEAKER_02] I zapravo puno ih je teže kontrolirati.

122
00:14:13,139 --> 00:14:14,919
[SPEAKER_02] A oni bi sve iskontrolirali.

123
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:17,200
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sad dolazimo zašto bi iskontrolirali.

124
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,840
[SPEAKER_02] Jer su nam ti sustavi.

125
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,039
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, ja volim ovako.

126
00:14:20,039 --> 00:14:21,679
[SPEAKER_02] Sad mi tu malo mikrofon smeta.

127
00:14:21,679 --> 00:14:24,399
[SPEAKER_02] Možeš ga malo ga, a nemoj puno da te nema veze.

128
