820
01:15:46,100 --> 01:15:48,300
[SPEAKER_02] Ima ih puno na tu temu.

821
01:15:48,300 --> 01:15:51,479
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, koje su onako nisu pretjerano agresivne.

822
